ets/steam/apps/1413480/extras/d82668bd5391aef833a63cabc3e403c1.mp4?t=1763531118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>深深吸引观众的艺术性，与现代社会也相通的故事带来的信息性，以及作为RPG的完成度，时至今日也毫不褪色。<br><br>本作的特点：<br><br>重置的3D模型和背景<br><br>追加的难度设定<br><br>中断保存功能-- 可以在任意时刻保存！<br><br>语音-- 可选择日语和英语语音<br><br>STEAM的成就与集换式卡牌<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1413480/extras/fe736f2dcaed527d2616f45ec6e86fdd.poster.avif?t=1763531118\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1413480/extras/fe736f2dcaed527d2616f45ec6e86fdd.webm?t=1763531118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1413480/extras/fe736f2dcaed527d2616f45ec6e86fdd.mp4?t=1763531118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
